{"tid":2332474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國安法又要出動] 警方通緝逃離伊利沙伯醫院63歲確診男子","createTime":"2020-12-19T15:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T15:08:58.000Z","uid":171302,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fc270cdd9d508be54d8aa3498755b60b31d5149f","tid":2332474,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T15:44:03.000Z","msg":"警方正通緝一名63歲確診新型肺炎男患者李運強，這名男子昨日下午擅自離開原本入住的伊利沙伯醫院，警方昨日接獲院方通報，表示正全力調查。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566183-20201219.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566183-20201219.htm&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=669607af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566183-20201219.htm&h=30b54be7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566183-20201219.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國安法條文如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fh0MbuF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFh0MbuF.png&h=4c89f2e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">條死廢老諗住用病毒攬炒全香港經濟，係咪恐怖活動？？萬用Key國安法係咪要出動</span><br />\n</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會證明冇晒反對派，點解建制派唔提議用國安法？係咪想助攻攬炒全香港經濟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc694877db210eaf05b2ef5a3ce7b63adc6af24","tid":2332474,"uid":170160,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T15:45:42.000Z","msg":"藍屍可能豁免任何刑責，仲會搭膊頭送番佢入院添 !? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1da1c0e2178c3731c5d51343892dabf204ed22","tid":2332474,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3cc694877db210eaf05b2ef5a3ce7b63adc6af24","tid":2332474,"uid":170160,