MRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=7c19906c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap599!zh-Hant-HK</a><br />\n因為佢中咗表列嘅傳染病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917b1c9f3f8b29ccb186eaa070c2aee77da29d0e","tid":2332474,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8701f62193e1c7c4162542616374a8dae1d26788","tid":2332474,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T15:56:11.000Z","msg":"其實犯左咩法？病左唔睇醫生都犯法？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T01:25:22.000Z","msg":"29.出入限制<br />\n(1)任何人不得離開該人被檢疫或隔離所在的地方。<br />\n(2)除衞生主任外，任何人不得在未獲根據第31條給予的書面准許下 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)進入另一人被檢疫或隔離所在的地方；或<br />\n(b)進入或離開受隔離的地方。<br />\n(3)任何人違反第(1)或(2)款，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處第2級罰款及監禁6個月。"},{"pid":"224d21d48f345bf3cd9b74b88419a06c14345b6e","tid":2332474,"uid":48026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T01:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3xhryj3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3xhryj3.gif&h=4b6ffb24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"058e72ca71e435c270496886154283ee5858231a","tid":2332474,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T01:41:46.000Z","msg":"搵人陪葬。地鐵啲扶手柱，升降機掣，商場門柄，全部高危"}]}